            "description": "Admin-only. Lists all users with the driver role, and saves the first one as driver_id. Note: this overwrites driver_id, which Login Driver also sets. Run this AFTER the Routes/Stops requests below if you want to keep testing with driver1, or run it any time if you just want to inspect the endpoint."
